body_html: @tung238 is your model trained with quantization? 'inference_type=QUANTIZED_UINT8' and 'quantize_weights' are not meant to be used at the same time. If your model was trained with quantization, use 'inference_type=QUANTIZED_UINT8' and remove 'quantize_weights'.
